  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to edit my wallet account's name, so that I can keep them updated upon my wish.\r\n\r\n#### Depends on: #17370\r\n\r\n### Design\r\n\r\n[Link to Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=884%3A221526&mode=design&t=HAPnaZA7OyKz1997-1)\r\n\r\n<img width=\"450\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/19339952/f9c052bf-0114-460d-8db4-831b9a1b30cb\" />\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\n- On tap of the account name in the edit account screen, the device's soft keyboard and `Update account name` button in the disabled state should be shown\r\n- If the account name doesn't pass the validation listed below, the error message should be displayed as per the design\r\n- On successful validation of the account name, the `Update account name` button should be enabled\r\n- On tap of the Update account name` button, the success toast should be displayed\r\n\r\n#### Account name validation\r\n\r\n- no emojis\r\n- no special character\r\n- name should be unique **\r\n- emoji and name combination should be unique ** \r\n\r\n** can use mock data to simulate the behaviour.\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\n- This issue doesn't update the account emoji in status-go. It will be handled separately later.\r\n",
